OL,3,CGovernment drops Troubles immunity
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,FThe UK Government has dropped an
OL,7,Fappeal against part of a court
OL,8,Fjudgment that struck out controversial
OL,9,Faspects of the previous
OL,10,Fadministration's Troubles legacy laws.
OL,12,FThe Labour Government has already
OL,13,Fvowed to repeal and replace the
OL,14,Flegislative provision introduced by
OL,15,Fthe last Conservative government that
OL,16,Foffered a form of conditional immunity
OL,17,Fto perpetrators of crimes during the
OL,18,Fconflict.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/19
