OL,3,CGovernment drops Troubles immunity
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,FImmunity was to be given to those
OL,7,Findividuals who cooperated with a new
OL,8,Ftruth recovery mechanism designed to
OL,9,Fprovide bereaved families answers
OL,10,Fabout the circumstances of their loved
OL,11,Fones' deaths.
OL,13,FLabour has also committed to reversing
OL,14,Fthe Legacy Act's contentious ban on
OL,15,Fcivil cases and inquests related to
OL,16,FTroubles incidents.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/19
