OL,3,CGovernment drops Troubles immunity
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,FIn February, a High Court judge in
OL,7,FBelfast declared several elements of
OL,8,Fthe Act incompatible with the European
OL,9,FConvention on Human Rights. The
OL,10,Fprovisions included the offer of
OL,11,Fconditional immunity and the
OL,12,Fdiscontinuation of civil cases and
OL,13,Finquests.
OL,15,FIn June, the previous government began
OL,16,Fa legal appeal against those findings.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/19
