OL,3,CGovernment drops Troubles immunity
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,FOn Monday, in a written statement to
OL,7,Fthe House of Commons, Northern Ireland
OL,8,FSecretary Hilary Benn confirmed his
OL,9,Fgovernment was dropping the appeal on
OL,10,Fthe incompatibility with the ECHR.
OL,12,F"This is the first step in fulfilling
OL,13,Fthe government's manifesto commitment
OL,14,Fto repeal and replace the Act," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/19
