OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F449A1722423502
OL,3,CGovernment drops Troubles immunity
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,F"Victims and survivors have felt
OL,7,Fignored by the previous government's
OL,8,Fapproach to legacy, which has been
OL,9,Fclearly rejected across communities in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland. The conditional
OL,11,Fimmunity provisions, in particular,
OL,12,Fhave been opposed by all of the
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland political parties and
OL,14,Fby many victims and survivors, as well
OL,15,Fas being found by the court to be
OL,16,Funlawful."
OL,18,FMr Benn said the move was evidence
OL,19,Fthat his government would adopt a
OL,20,F"different approach" to legacy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@JO]|D@AOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
