PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F449A1722423503
OL,3,CGovernment drops Troubles immunity
OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,F"It underlines the government's
OL,7,Fabsolute commitment to the Human
OL,8,FRights Act, and to establishing legacy
OL,9,Fmechanisms that are capable of
OL,10,Fcommanding the confidence of
OL,11,Fcommunities and of victims and
OL,12,Fsurvivors," he added.
OL,14,FMr Benn said the government would
OL,15,Fbegin preparations to address the
OL,16,Ffindings of the High Court, which will
OL,17,Finclude laying a draft remedial order
OL,18,Fin Parliament under section 10 of the
OL,19,FHuman Rights Act 1998 to remove
OL,20,Foffending provisions from the statute
OL,21,Fbook.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/19
