OL,4,Cappeal
OL,6,FHe said the draft order would be laid
OL,7,F"as soon as parliamentary time allows".
OL,9,FThe court ruling in February also
OL,10,Ffound that the Legacy Act breached
OL,11,Felements of the post-Brexit
OL,12,Farrangements for Northern Ireland `
OL,13,Fthe Windsor Framework.
OL,15,FArticle 29 (1) of the framework states
OL,16,Fthat the government must ensure that
OL,17,Fvarious rights entitlements in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland, which were enshrined
OL,19,Ffollowing the Good Friday Agreement of
OL,20,F1998, cannot be diminished as a result
OL,21,Fof the UK leaving the EU.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/19
