OL,6,F"Therefore, we have asked the court to
OL,7,Fcontinue with its consideration of the
OL,8,Finterpretation and effect of Article
OL,9,F2(1) given the profound constitutional
OL,10,Fand legal questions that have arisen
OL,11,Ffrom the ruling."
OL,13,FMr Benn said the ongoing appeal
OL,14,Frelated to a "technical point of law"
OL,15,Fwhich he hoped could be clarified to
OL,16,Fensure "legal certainty" around the
OL,17,Fhuman rights framework in Northern
OL,18,FIreland.
