OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland Troubles (Legacy
OL,7,Fand Reconciliation) Act passed into
OL,8,Flaw last September.
OL,10,FFrom May 1 this year, all civil cases
OL,11,Fand inquests that were not at their
OL,12,Ffindings stage were halted.
OL,14,FResponsibility for investigating all
OL,15,Flegacy cases was also transferred to a
OL,16,Fnew truth recovery body, the
OL,17,FIndependent Commission for
OL,18,FReconciliation and Information
OL,19,FRecovery (ICRIR).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/19
