OL,6,F"The success of the ICRIR will,
OL,7,Fultimately, be determined by its
OL,8,Fability to deliver justice,
OL,9,Faccountability, and information to
OL,10,Fvictims and survivors of the
OL,11,FTroubles," he said.
OL,13,F"Under the leadership of (former Lord
OL,14,FChief Justice for Northern Ireland)
OL,15,FSir Declan Morgan as Chief
OL,16,FCommissioner, the Government has
OL,17,Fconfidence in its ability to do so.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@JO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/19
