OL,6,F"It is also clear, however, that to
OL,7,Fachieve these objectives, the ICRIR
OL,8,Fwill need to gain the confidence of
OL,9,Fvictims and survivors in its work.
OL,11,F"The government will consult on
OL,12,Fmeasures to strengthen the ICRIR's
OL,13,Findependence from government and its
OL,14,Fpowers."
