OL,6,FIn regard to ending the ban on civil
OL,7,Fproceedings and inquests, Mr Benn
OL,8,Fadded: "The government is acutely
OL,9,Faware of the distress that the
OL,10,Fcessation of live inquests in
OL,11,Fparticular has caused those families,
OL,12,Fand will consider all possible options
OL,13,Fto ensure those cases can conclude
OL,14,Fsatisfactorily.
OL,16,F"We will also consider the best way
OL,17,Fforward for those inquests involving a
OL,18,Fsignificant amount of sensitive
OL,19,Finformation which were unable to
OL,20,Fconclude within the coronial system."
