OL,6,FMr Benn stressed the importance of
OL,7,Faddressing the legacy of the past in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,10,F"The government recognises that
OL,11,Fachieving absolute consensus on these
OL,12,Fissues is immensely difficult," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"That is demonstrated by the series of
OL,16,Ffailed attempts since 1998 to
OL,17,Fimplement effective legacy mechanisms.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@_O]wD@AOU
