OL,6,F"Indeed, even the Good Friday
OL,7,FAgreement, which brought peace to
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland after decades of
OL,9,Fviolence, was opposed by some due to
OL,10,Fthe very challenging policy of
OL,11,Freleasing early from prison those
OL,12,Findividuals convicted for serious
OL,13,FTroubles-related offences."
OL,15,FMr Benn said a consultation exercise
OL,16,Fwould be undertaken to gauge the views
OL,17,Fof victims and survivors.
