OL,6,F"This will, of course, include
OL,7,Fengagement with the Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fpolitical parties and with the Irish
OL,9,FGovernment, with whom the UK
OL,10,FGovernment is committed to working in
OL,11,Fpartnership in seeking a practical way
OL,12,Fforward that can command support
OL,13,Facross communities in Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fand beyond," he said.
