OL,6,F"This will include veterans,
OL,7,Frecognising the dedicated service of
OL,8,Fthe vast majority of police officers,
OL,9,Fmembers of the armed forces, and the
OL,10,Fsecurity services who did so much to
OL,11,Fkeep people in Northern Ireland safe
OL,12,Fduring the Troubles.
OL,14,F"The government recognises that this
OL,15,Fprocess will involve difficult
OL,16,Fconversations, and that many
OL,17,Fstakeholders will hold different views
OL,18,Fregarding the best way forward.
